text: Ummendorf is a municipality in Biberach in Baden-Württemberg in Germany. It is on the main route of the Upper Swabian Baroque Route (Oberschwäbische Barockstraße). == Sights == * Catholic church Johanneskirche, 1805 * Castle Ummendorfer Schloss, 1560 * Castle Schloss Horn at Fischbach == References == Category:Biberach (district)
title: Ummendorf, Baden-Württemberg
